    "long_instructions": "### Choose a Song\r\n\r\nNow it's your turn to take everything you've learned and make it your own! In this level, you'll explore, experiment, and build a live performance using loops, triggers, and effects.\r\n\r\nIf you want to pick a new song, you can click the restart button in the upper-right corner [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=start-over-button)\r\n\r\n**Do This**:\r\n- Set up your sound - Create a backing track or start from scratch.\r\n- Use triggers - Add sounds, loops, or effects in real-time to shape your performance.\r\n- Create variations - Experiment with filters, timing, and layering to make your music dynamic.\r\n- Perform live! Play around, improvise, and see where the music takes you.\r\n\r\n",
